body_html: @jlinleung can you confirm that you don't have multiple versions in different paths? Maybe installing a clean version in a new conda/python environment would resolve it. Alternatively (and this can be dangerous) you might want to VERY CAREFULLY delete any folder in your path that contains 'tensorflow' in the name.
